    "body": "Thanks for reporting this. I think the problem is that the hardhat-ganache plugin is not handling type extensions like the rest of the plugins do. As a temporary workaround, you can either use a js config or add a `// @ts-ignore` comment in the line before the one that has the `dbPath` field.",
